    "Pathways towards more informative representations have hitherto followed two main directions.",
    "Methods have pursued the model of augmented scale, where increasing model capacity monotonically increases performance 22.",
    "While initial language models reached tens of millions 23 or hundreds of millions 24 of parameters, later developments have seen models with over 5 billion weights 19, 25, 26 with parameter counts exceeding the size of the training set.",
